## üõ†Ô∏è Hardware & Build Summaries

- **Hull Design:**  
  - Original: 62"x124"x28", Al, TUFROC shell, ‚Äúcandy mint‚Äù oval, white/smooth/tapered.
  - Scaled: 42% smaller for test hulls.  
  - Mount: Telescoping 12‚Äì24", 5" shaft, 180¬∞ rotation.
- **Coil:**  
  - 300 turns/section, graphene+NbTi windings, 8-section, copper tori dividers, cryo (77K).
- **Tri-Grate/Grid:**  
  - At end of last winding, 6"x26"x60" (scaled for mini-hulls), 70% iron composite.
- **Sphere Test Ball:**  
  - 8ft dia, TUFROC, platform-mounted, lithium pack, control box, ring for hull mounts.

